{"tid":4592,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求意見]東京8日+滑雪行程","createTime":"2016-11-26T14:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T10:35:52.000Z","uid":16902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1389ca4a73cdccb444aacafc280864822b5c483c","tid":4592,"uid":16902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"Day 1:<br />\n21:00抵達成田國際機場  &rarr; 京成成田站 &rarr; 住APA<br />\n--因為個日過埋關都幾夜,所以我地住係附近京成成田站既APA<br />\n<br />\nDay2:<br />\n京成成田站  &rarr; lunch :駿河屋 SURUGAYA アクセスマップ &rarr;check out &rarr;井澤站&rarr;住(輕井澤站)APA<br />\n--因為我地諗住去滑雪,而上網搵發覺'井澤'個到有滑雪場,所以決定去井澤個到住1晚 另一朝就去滑雪<br />\n<br />\nDay3:<br />\n輕井澤站 &rarr;check out(行李放lobby) &rarr;輕井澤波希米亞玻璃美術館 &rarr;輕井澤王子大酒店滑雪場&rarr; 新宿 &rarr;住(新宿) BNB<br />\n--新宿呢間bnb 應該就會住到尾 其實小弟都係想搵返近東京附近嘅地方住<br />\n而本身呢個行程啲$大部份都想放係食嗰度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以想問 住新宿係咪個好選擇？ 例如其實邊個地區多宵夜同方便 ⁠⁠⁠⁠</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\nDay4:<br />\n新宿 &rarr;  上野 &rarr;  淺草 &rarr;  淺草寺，雷門，晴空塔  &rarr; dinner: 新宿燒肉放題:六歌仙 / 放題食燒牛-しゃぶ禪&rarr;新宿  /<br />\n新宿 &rarr;  高尾山 &rarr; 秋葉原 &rarr; 東京駅 &rarr; 東京鐵塔 &rarr; dinner: 新宿燒肉放題:六歌仙 /放題食燒牛-しゃぶ禪&rarr;新宿<br />\n--呢日想問 行邊條路線好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  會唔會太chur<br />\n同埋係咪寧願去東京鐵塔都好過去晴空塔??? <br />\n<br />\nDay5:<br />\n新宿&rarr; 墨田水族&rarr;池袋 &rarr; Sunshine City &rarr; dinner: 無敵家拉面 &rarr;新宿<br />\n--呢一日想shopping同睇水族館為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay6:<br />\n新宿 &rarr;  Disney&rarr; 東京新宿釣船茶屋 Zauo 釣船茶屋 &rarr;新宿<br />\n<br />\nDay7:<br />\n新宿&rarr;築地 排(壽司大)&rarr; 跟住行下場外市場 (breakfast + lunch)  &rarr;  ?? &rarr; 銀座 &rarr;dinner :お好み焼 道とん堀 &rarr; 新宿<br />\n--呢日想問 通常去完築地 之後有咩路程推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay8:<br />\ncheck out 新宿&rarr; 成田國際機場 9:00am離境<br />\n--因為9點飛機起飛 <span style=\"color: red;\">小弟想問有無咩交通工具 可以係深夜可以到成田機場? </span>"},{"pid":"e0135f40a3d034046cbc14b136d874c037680349","tid":4592,"uid":16902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a215cc9bba29b9b3b04c80a996efc38ea82f6c81","tid":4592,"uid":16902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c696ec0536ac1f80e7efc8b5c82ec9fa95e203","tid":4592,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的士幫到你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真..好似有凌晨巴不過班次唔多"},{"pid":"2c22799b40581f0667bc553d44c9dfc6d5eafdd5","tid":4592,"uid":16902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的士幫到你<br />\n認真..好似有凌晨巴不過班次唔多</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n應該會搭凌晨巴士"},{"pid":"dd2f1b35089d2151fc75c4d42323d2b0c780eeb4","tid":4592,"uid":16902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f8dd93f7f290c6081269b08678ee1821887e19","tid":4592,"uid":16869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<br />\n留名"},{"pid":"19d930fe83eaac081a6a6d04a8d300a10aaeaf46","tid":4592,"uid":16869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1eb2373988b91362643c9dc77edf887c992cc1","tid":4592,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T18:26:53.000Z","msg":"留名 <br />\n巴打是咪搭hkairline? 因為我1月去都係呢個航班時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122fd4950a4dab3536d46d40dfb4c0605f813525","tid":4592,"uid":16902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T18:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名 <br />\n巴打是咪搭hkairline? 因為我1月去都係呢個航班時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀巴打<br />\n巴打plan左咩行程 一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5bbbedd9df02d42439aedd1af26c77f3831200","tid":4592,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T18:49:27.000Z","msg":"呢排好多assignment乜都未plan 連酒店都未book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過應該會去近郊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走前一晚諗緊去大江戶溫泉物語過夜好唔好"},{"pid":"1109db8a431a77af5ea2aef8bf1e4134aa11d158","tid":4592,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T23:48:05.000Z","msg":"一月壽司大搬左未"},{"pid":"d151d2b2e9ffdf09f891729adec8ea1b6a92ec5b","tid":4592,"uid":26520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T23:55:06.000Z","msg":"壽司大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi